<div class="container">
  <!-- Main jumbotron for a primary marketing message or call to action -->
    <div class="jumbotron">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to my blog</h1>
        <p>Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada fames ac turpis egestas. Vestibulum tortor quam, feugiat vitae, ultricies eget, tempor sit amet, ante. Donec eu libero sit amet quam egestas semper.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="../register" role="button">Admin Register &raquo;</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3>Tags :</h3><% if !@tags.nil? %><% @tags.each do |tag|%><a href=""><%=tag.name %> ,</a><%end%><%end%>
    </div>
    
 

    <div class="container">
      <!-- Example row of columns -->
      <div class="row">
        <table class="table table-hover">

          <tr>
            <th>Posts</th>
            <th>Created by</th>
          </tr>
          <% if !@posts.nil? %>
            <% @posts.each do |post|%>
              <tr>
                <td><a href="/post/<%=post.id %>"><%=post.title %></a><p><%= post.post %></p></td>
                <td><p><%=post.user.email %></p></td>
              </tr>
            <% end %>
          <% end %>
        </table>
      </div>

      <hr>

      <footer>
        <p>&copy; Company 2014</p>
      </footer>
    </div> <!-- /container -->
</div>